title: Starts of the Week + Week 2 Breakdown, The Dump Truck - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/15
description:
Week 2 kicks off tonight! On today’s fantasy football podcast, lots of Week 2 matchup previews and Starts of the Week from Andy, Mike, and Jason! Plus, injury updates, and a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 15th, 2022.
